CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781215878
OL,3,C'Game-changing' Wegovy weight loss
OL,4,Cpill approved for use in the UK
OL,6,FA Wegovy weight loss pill has been
OL,7,Fapproved for private use in the UK for
OL,8,Fthe first time.
OL,10,FThe GLP-1 pill is taken daily, and
OL,11,Fdesigned for obese adults with a body
OL,12,Fmass index (BMI) of 30 or above,
OL,13,Fincluding those who might have related
OL,14,Fconditions, such as high blood
OL,15,Fpressure.
OL,17,FThe starting dose for the tablet is
OL,18,F1.5mg, rising to 4mg, 9mg and 25mg,
OL,19,Fwith patients needing to be on each
OL,20,Fdose level for a month before they
OL,21,Fincrease it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
