FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781215878
OL,3,C'Game-changing' Wegovy weight loss
OL,4,Cpill approved for use in the UK
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FPeople currently being treated
OL,12,Fprivately with a 2.4mg Wegovy
OL,13,Finjection once a week can move
OL,14,Fstraight to 25mg tablets once per day,
OL,15,Fthe Medicines and Healthcare products
OL,16,FRegulatory Agency (MHRA) said.
OL,18,FThe drug is given on prescription and
OL,19,Fwill be available privately within
OL,20,Fweeks, but has not yet been assessed
OL,21,Ffor use on the NHS.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781215878
OL,3,C'Game-changing' Wegovy weight loss
OL,4,Cpill approved for use in the UK
OL,6,FThe MHRA has approved the drug based
OL,7,Fon data from a trial where adults were
OL,8,Fgiven 25mg per day in addition to diet
OL,9,Fand exercise.
OL,11,FAdults taking the pill lost an average
OL,12,Fof 17% of their body weight after 64
OL,13,Fweeks, compared with 3% for people on
OL,14,Fa dummy drug.
OL,16,F"This marks an important milestone for
OL,17,Fobesity care in the UK," said Sebnem
OL,18,FAvsar Tuna, general manager at Novo
OL,19,FNordisk, who made the tablet.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
