PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781215878
OL,3,C'Game-changing' Wegovy weight loss
OL,4,Cpill approved for use in the UK
OL,6,F"For the first time, people living
OL,7,Fwith obesity have access to a GLP-1
OL,8,Ftreatment in a daily pill, allowing
OL,9,Fthem the choice and flexibility of
OL,10,Foral treatment to support their long-
OL,11,Fterm weight management."
OL,13,FJulian Beach, executive director of
OL,14,Fhealthcare quality and access at the
OL,15,FMHRA, said the tablet met the agency's
OL,16,F"rigorous standards of safety, quality
OL,17,Fand effectiveness".
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
