PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781215878
OL,3,C'Game-changing' Wegovy weight loss
OL,4,Cpill approved for use in the UK
OL,6,FThe tablet should be taken whole on an
OL,7,Fempty stomach with a sip of water
OL,8,Fafter a fasting period of at least
OL,9,Feight hours, and no food or drink can
OL,10,Fbe consumed within 30 minutes after.
OL,12,FThe medication can have some side-
OL,13,Feffects, however, with the most common
OL,14,Fsymptoms including nausea, diarrhoea,
OL,15,Fconstipation, and vomiting.
OL,17,FJames O'Loan, chief executive of
OL,18,FChemist4U, described the launch of the
OL,19,Ftablet as "game-changing" for UK
OL,20,Fpatients.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
