FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781215878
OL,3,C'Game-changing' Wegovy weight loss
OL,4,Cpill approved for use in the UK
OL,6,F"We've already seen record demand
OL,7,Fahead of the expected launch of a
OL,8,FWegovy pill in the coming months, with
OL,9,Fover 10,000 people joining our waiting
OL,10,Flist for a consultation," O'Loan said.
OL,12,F"Notably, the majority of people
OL,13,Fexpressing interest in the launch of
OL,14,Fweight loss pills have not previously
OL,15,Fused GLP-1s, indicating that the
OL,16,Flaunch could widen access to millions
OL,17,Fof people across the country.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
