OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781215878
OL,3,C'Game-changing' Wegovy weight loss
OL,4,Cpill approved for use in the UK
OL,6,F"Weight loss pills are a great
OL,7,Falternative for people who don't feel
OL,8,Fcomfortable using injections and many
OL,9,Fwill find that a daily pill feels more
OL,10,Ffamiliar and easier to fit into their
OL,11,Froutine.
OL,13,F"We expect that demand for weight loss
OL,14,Fpills will only increase as
OL,15,Fprospective patients become aware of
OL,16,Fthem in the coming weeks and months."
